{"tid":2487930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澄清一下，政府唔係禁止投廢票，只係禁止「煽惑他人」投廢票","createTime":"2021-04-14T02:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T02:54:55.000Z","uid":24730,"like":12,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"741df96b5ebb561d669494793e7e04e93b1cf222","tid":2487930,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:02:04.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">呢排成日聽到人講政府禁止選民唔投票、投白票或廢票，搞到個個都唔知點好。而家澄清一下，政府好寬宏大量嘅，並冇禁止大家咁做，只係要立法禁止「<span class=\"red\">煽惑他人</span>不投票、投白票或廢票」，希望大家唔好咁驚</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「林鄭表明將修訂《選舉（舞弊及非法行為）條例》，如任何人在選舉期間內藉公開活動煽惑他人不投票、投白票或廢票，即屬干犯非法行為；任何人故意妨礙或阻止另一人在選舉中投票，即干犯舞弊行為。」"},{"pid":"681de1f31350bf869a7b426abbc68430a490d8a4","tid":2487930,"uid":173666,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:03:13.000Z","msg":"咁既然投廢票冇問題 點解唔可以叫人投廢票"},{"pid":"82074ca91d09a7214198c61d3e4dfa7fd5bb9232","tid":2487930,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"681de1f31350bf869a7b426abbc68430a490d8a4","tid":2487930,"uid":173666,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:03:13.000Z","msg":"咁既然投廢票冇問題 點解唔可以叫人投廢票"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:04:35.000Z","msg":"真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae3baf5786e66b61a5a5c79d8eb99151ea5c0da","tid":2487930,"uid":216163,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:05:13.000Z","msg":"叫人做合法行為=犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ca2aa29bbb83255dd3a627069efca52ff07a72","tid":2487930,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:05:43.000Z","msg":"藍絲總動員可以將投票率谷到25-30%"},{"pid":"8a3bbd4ea3b899043b90edb194d9a11dcdfba904","tid":2487930,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"681de1f31350bf869a7b426abbc68430a490d8a4","tid":2487930,"uid":173666,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:03:13.000Z","msg":"咁既然投廢票冇問題 點解